metadata.name: glass car #01
metadata.description: Introducing the "Glassiverse" collection, where a whimsical world of glass comes alive! Embark on an enchanting journey through a universe crafted entirely from glass. These delightful toy cars, suspended in mid-air by fluffy clouds, invite you to experience a dreamlike adventure like no other. Every piece in this collection showcases the artistry and wonder of glass, creating a magical spectacle that will captivate hearts around the world. Get ready to explore the Glassiverse and discover the joy of a transparent and extraordinary realm!
